---
# lootlib
-- library to produce loot for the mia roguelike
# item ideas
-- below are some ideas for items
--- these are here for later reference
---- demon's blood
-- can be used for as a material or item to sell
-- should drop from demons or be purchased
---- blood sword -- forged from the blood of a demon
-- can be forged from demon's blood or via random drop chance
---- blood sword of imprisonment -- forged by an imprisoned demon from it's own blood
-- can only be obtained via random drop or by defeating an escapist demon
---- 
# notes
-- this library /will/ depend on the psh-prng and rbuilder submods
-- please clone with `--recursive`
